"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-lifestyle-trending-paris-2024-olympics-opening-ceremony-organisers-apologise-for-offence-caused-by-religious-scene-news-story-42f5de5eb28babb39214c4915e866b03\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 Olympics organisers have apologised after a scene from the opening ceremony depicting religious imagery sparked controversy among commentators and the Catholic Church.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 162, \"end\": 177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999726214813, \"rank\": 2.6812199865797688e-08, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 Summer Olympics organisers have issued an apology following backlash over religious depictions during the opening ceremony on Friday, with commentators pointing out the hypocrisy of those behind the stunt.\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A tableau entitled \\\"Festivity\\\" drew criticism for appearing to depict Leonardo da Vinci's painting of The Last Supper, showing Jesus Christ with his apostles.\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8705881308897555e-24, \"text\": \"Leonardo da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}, {\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999947308424, \"rank\": 5.269234584325345e-09, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversial segment of the opening ceremony featured singer Philippe Katerine painted blue and almost naked while surrounded by drag queens and models.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 624, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philippe Katerine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippe_Katerine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After condemnation from politicians and religious groups, including the Catholic Church in France, organisers of the ceremony apologised for causing offence.\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999726214813, \"rank\": 2.6812199865797688e-08, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999892702364, \"rank\": 5.3770898917558445e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The interpretation of the Greek God Dionysus makes us aware of the absurdity of violence between human beings.#Paris2024#OpeningCeremonypic.twitter.com/FBlQNNUmvV  Sky News journalist Caroline Marcus said while no religion was above scrutiny, the stunt exposed the glaring hypocrisy of so-called progressives, who would never dare to satirise Islam.\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9928480934586613, \"rank\": 0.003088102973776548, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 912, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.418895369976189e-21, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}, {\"begin\": 1040, \"end\": 1048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999574433796, \"rank\": 4.25566740513168e-08, \"text\": \"Sky News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\"}, {\"begin\": 1060, \"end\": 1068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_literature\", \"score\": 0.9991512432272971, \"rank\": 0.0008494377599036179, \"text\": \"Caroline\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_literature\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/English_literature\"}, {\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 3.349353636025888e-11, \"text\": \"Marcus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marcus_Aurelius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No religion or ideology should be above mockery or satire ... it is the inconsistency which seems to be applied,\\\" she said on Sunday Showdown.\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Have some courage, try it with Islam, what would happen?\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You would have a fatwa slapped on your head faster than Ariarne Titmus can swim the 400 metre freestyle.\\\"\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1486, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariarne Titmus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariarne_Titmus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokeswoman Anne Descamps said: \\\"It is clear that there was never any intention to show disrespect to any religious group\\\"  Speaking at a press conference on Sunday, Ms Descamps added: \\\"I think (with artistic director) Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.182989481679978e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}, {\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offence we are, of course, really, really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Jolly, however, defended the flamboyant scene and told French media: \\\"You will never find in my work a desire to denigrate anyone or anything.\\\"\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2065, \"end\": 2071, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999962289564955, \"rank\": 3.659483232964329e-06, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Commentators have broadly condemned the \\\"woke\\\" opening ceremony with scenes that \\\"seek to ridicule Christians\\\".\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9697928090594233, \"rank\": 0.026970840776910924, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The scene was harshly criticised by French politicians as well as the French episcopal conference.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2304, \"end\": 2310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999962289564955, \"rank\": 3.659483232964329e-06, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999962289564955, \"rank\": 3.659483232964329e-06, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French politician Marion Mar\\u00e9chal described the ceremony as \\\"crude woke propaganda\\\" and said the event was taken \\\"ideologically hostage\\\" by left-wing activists.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9999962289564955, \"rank\": 3.659483232964329e-06, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2386, \"end\": 2401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marion_Mar\\u00e9chal\", \"score\": 0.9999998162447978, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marion Mar\\u00e9chal\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marion_Mar\\u00e9chal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marion_Mar\\u00e9chal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Catholic Church of France also expressed its disapproval and said: \\\"Unfortunately, this ceremony contained scenes that mocked Christianity, which we deeply regret.\\\"\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2534, \"end\": 2549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999726214813, \"rank\": 2.6812199865797688e-08, \"text\": \"Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 2553, \"end\": 2559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999892702364, \"rank\": 5.3770898917558445e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2660, \"end\": 2672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9970439862985325, \"rank\": 0.002964777622078168, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although, the statement added there were also \\\"wonderful moments of beauty and joy, rich in emotion and universally recognised\\\".\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Communiqu\\u00c3\\u00a9 de presse au sujet de la c\\u00c3\\u00a9r\\u00c3\\u00a9monie d\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122ouverture des Jeux olympiquespic.twitter.com/jUeB5uPHxp  French President Emmanuel Macron and his government have celebrated the event's success as more than 80 per cent of France held positive views about the ceremony.\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 3102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2940, \"end\": 2956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 2957, \"end\": 2972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 3056, \"end\": 3062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999892702364, \"rank\": 5.3770898917558445e-09, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Merci \\u00c3\\u00a0 Thomas Jolly et son g\\u00c3\\u00a9nie cr\\u00c3\\u00a9atif pour cette c\\u00c3\\u00a9r\\u00c3\\u00a9monie grandiose.\", \"from\": 3104, \"to\": 3182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Merci aux artistes pour ce moment unique et magique.\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Merci aux forces de l\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122ordre et de secours, aux agents et b\\u00c3\\u00a9n\\u00c3\\u00a9voles.\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Merci \\u00c3\\u00a0 tous ceux qui y ont cru.On en reparlera dans 100 ans\\u00c2\\u00a0!ON L\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u2122A FAIT\\u00c2\\u00a0!\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3357, \"end\": 3361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}, {\"begin\": 3372, \"end\": 3374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\", \"score\": 0.9984969607849297, \"rank\": 0.0013800897898592686, \"text\": \"ON\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ontario\"}, {\"begin\": 3375, \"end\": 3377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L\\u00e2\", \"score\": 0.669467902590356, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"L\\u00e2\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L\\u00e2\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L\\u00e2\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thanks to Thomas Jolly and his creative genius for this grandiose ceremony,\\\" President Macron wrote on X.\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3401, \"end\": 3407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.9997568125808333, \"rank\": 0.00024311597575229948, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}, {\"begin\": 3468, \"end\": 3484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"President Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you to the artists for this unique and magical moment\\u2026 We will be talking about it in 100 years' time!\\\"\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To join the conversation, pleaselog in.Do not have an account?Register  Join the conversation, you are commenting asLogout  Our Apps\", \"from\": 3610, \"to\": 3742, \"entities\": []}]}"